name: USB Type-C Hub
description: Easy use 3-in-1 USB Type-C Hub is made of aluminum alloy and comes in ABS housing. It offers 1x HDMI + 1x USB 3.0 + 1x USB Type C PD 2.0 interface. The Hoco HB14 supports PD2.0, working voltage / current 5V-20V / 3A, and maximum output power of 67W with a Type-C female socket. USB female socket: USB3.0 support maximum 0.75A. This hub is compatible with most operating systems, such as Windows and Mac OS. The Hoco HB14 comes with a 1 Month Warranty (Must Claim With Box & All Accessories).

name: Wireless ANC Headphone
description: The Wireless ANC Headphone features 40mm + 20mm Dual Taps Design that offers True Stereo Sounds. It is equipped with a high-quality Bluetooth Chip. Bluetooth 5.0 is more stable and faster than Bluetooth 4.2. It features multi-mode features. ANC Mode, Transparent Mode, and Normal Mode. M Key is easy to switch to the transparent mode for hearing what's happening around you. The WiWU Pilot Headphone offers Active Noise Cancellation for immersive sound.

name: Bluetooth 5.1 Earbuds
description: Airbuds 3 SE is the 3rd generation of earbuds with some attractive features like Audio Sharing, Instant connectivity, Pinch perfect control, longer battery life and many more but Spatial Audio feature is not included in the Special edition like base edition.. It also gives a real-time power display and adaptive EQ in-ear detection sensor.

name: Waterproof Smartwatch
description: 3 Smartwatch features a 1.71" IPS screen with a resolution of 280*320 for a fine display. The larger screen gives you more content. The front of the watch is fully covered by a 3D curved glass with crystal clear colors and a high-strength tempered glass that is scratch and wear-resistant without the need for a protective film. The body of the watch features a diamond-cut, right-angled metal center frame, with a powerful texture that is easy to reach.

name: Smart Air Purifier
description: Smart Air Purifier 4 Lite Filter with Voice Control has a particle CADR of up to 360m³/h and is able to deliver 6000L of clean air per minute. Powerful purification speeds keep the air in your home cleaner for longer. The air is filled with pollutants that pose a risk to your health. The Xiaomi Smart Air Purifier 4 Lite features a three-in-one filter, it is capable of 99.97% filtration of 0.3μm particles, and layer-by-layer filtration of air pollutants.

name: Case for iPhone
description: Transparent Soft Phone Case is specially designed for iPhone 7/8, Here added 4 shock absorption airbags. There are 4 separate airbags on the corners of UGREEN iPhone 7/8 clear case, which helps to protecting your phone from possible crashes, even if your phone falls from a 10m high place. Raised 0.35mm of camera and screen edges, lift screen and camera off flat surfaces, add one more protection for the screen and camera.

name: USB Web Camera
description: Webcam has clear calls and an inbuilt microphone. It has an adjustable tilt and a broad field of view. No drivers are needed; just plug and play. It uses SENSOR technology with a COMS1/4 color chip. A 1G3P HD camera is being used. The file formats for this webcam are MJPG/YUY2/BMP/JPEG/PNG/AVI/WMV, and the transmission speeds are 1280 x 720 and 1920 x 1080.

name: Fast Charging Power Bank
description: 10000mAh 22.5W Fast Charging Power Bank is the perfect addition to any mobile device user’s toolkit. It has a Li-polymer battery With 10000mAh 3.85V (38.5Wh) Capacity. This power bank features a built-in Large LED Digital Display that shows the remaining battery life and charging status. It also has three output ports, where it has two USB-A outputs, one USB-C input/output, and one Micro USB input, making it compatible with a variety of devices.
